The Frood
=========

*Author* [Jens Riisom Schultz](mailto:jers@fynskemedier.dk)
*Since*  2011-06-20

The Frood standardizes MVC in Xoops.

It will help you to:

  * Add MVC code to existing modules without breaking existing functionality.
  * Refactor modules to MVC.
  * Create entirely new full fledged MVC modules.
  * Communicate with other Froody modules, using MVC without the overhead and
    hassle of http requests.


Documentation
-------------

All of the compiled documentation for The Frood can be found
[here](http://vserver10.fynskemedier.dk:8080/cruisecontrol/buildresults/frood?tab=documentation)

  * See INSTALL for installation instructions.
  * See TUTORIAL for instructions on how to code with The Frood.
  * See CHANGELOG for a change log.
